<h2>Welcome Chess Parents!</h2>

<div class="row">
	<div class="small-7 columns">

<p><%= image_tag 'index.jpeg', class: "left" %> Welcome to Alex & Mark Chess Camp webpage
all of our instructors have exceptionally high ratings. You can get a lot out from joining our camp. We have navigation bar at the top and you can take a look about the details of our camp.
</p>

</div>



